arStrings.szText: Your Shapeshifting Skills are dealing increased damage.

{c_important}Lacerate{/c} hits Heal for {c_number}[{SF_14}*100|%|]{/c} Maximum Life {c_number}([PlayerHealthMax() * SF_14]){/c}, doubled on Critical Strikes. The first Critical Strike is guaranteed and deals {c_number}[{SF_15}*100|%x|]{/c} increased damage.

Whenever {c_important}Lacerate{/c} Critically Strikes, your {c_important}Shapeshifting{/c} Skills deal {c_number}[{SF_17}*100|%x|]{/c} increased damage for {c_number}{SF_18}{/c} seconds, up to {c_number}[{SF_20}*100|%x|]{/c}.
